
to install:

just extract the archive to /celestia ( $CELESTIA_ROOT )
or copy /extras/JohnVV to /celestia ( $CELESTIA_ROOT )

the EarthSpec.zip extracts to:

`-- extras
    `-- JohnVV
        |-- EarthSpec.ssc
        `-- textures
            |-- hires
            |   `-- EarthSpec.png
            |-- lores
            |   `-- EarthSpec.png
            `-- medres
                `-- EarthSpec.png


The orig. earth map that the specular map was made from ,I think, BlueMarble and made in 2004 

